@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Privacy Policy";
}

<!-- Add style block to make the background black and text white -->
<style>
    body {
        background-color: black; /* Black background */
        color: white; /* White text */
    }

    h1, h2 {
        color: lightgreen; /* Light green headings */
    }

    a {
        color: lightblue; /* Light blue for links */
    }

    a:hover {
        color: white; /* White on hover for links */
    }

    .text-muted {
        color: grey; /* Muted text in grey */
    }

    .btn {
        background-color: lightgreen;
        border-color: lightgreen;
        color: black; /* Black text on buttons */
    }

    .btn:hover {
        background-color: green;
        border-color: green;
        color: white; /* White text on hover */
    }
</style>

<div class="container mt-5">
    <h1 class="display-4">@ViewData["Title"]</h1>
    <p class="lead">Your privacy is important to us. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, disclose, and safeguard your information when you visit our website.</p>

    <h2 class="mt-4">1. Information We Collect</h2>
    <p>We may collect personal information that you voluntarily provide to us when you register on the site, subscribe to a newsletter, or engage in certain activities. This includes:</p>
    <ul class="list-unstyled lead">
        <li>📝 <strong>Personal Data</strong>: Name, email address, phone number, etc.</li>
        <li>🔒 <strong>Usage Data</strong>: IP address, browser type, pages visited, time spent, etc.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2 class="mt-4">2. How We Use Your Information</h2>
    <p>We use the information we collect from you in the following ways:</p>
    <ul class="list-unstyled lead">
        <li>⚙️ To personalize your experience and deliver custom content</li>
        <li>📩 To send periodic emails regarding updates or other relevant information</li>
        <li>🔐 To improve our website and provide better services</li>
    </ul>

    <h2 class="mt-4">3. Sharing Your Information</h2>
    <p>We do not sell, trade, or otherwise transfer to outside parties your personally identifiable information. However, we may share your information with:</p>
    <ul class="list-unstyled lead">
        <li>🤝 Trusted third parties who assist us in operating our website</li>
        <li>⚖️ Law enforcement or government authorities, if required by law</li>
    </ul>

    <h2 class="mt-4">4. Cookies & Tracking Technologies</h2>
    <p>We use cookies to help us understand how visitors interact with our site. These technologies are used for:</p>
    <ul class="list-unstyled lead">
        <li>🍪 <strong>Essential Cookies</strong>: Necessary for basic website functionality</li>
        <li>📊 <strong>Analytics</strong>: To track and measure usage and performance</li>
    </ul>

    <h2 class="mt-4">5. Your Privacy Rights</h2>
    <p>You have the right to access, correct, or delete the personal information we have collected about you. If you wish to exercise any of these rights, please contact us at:</p>
    <p><strong>Email:</strong> <a href="mailto:privacy@yourwebsite.com">privacy@yourwebsite.com</a></p>

    <h2 class="mt-4">6. Security of Your Information</h2>
    <p>We implement security measures to protect your personal data. While we strive to use the highest level of security, no method of data transmission or storage is 100% secure. As such, we cannot guarantee absolute security.</p>

    <h2 class="mt-4">7. Changes to This Privacy Policy</h2>
    <p>We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time to reflect changes in our practices or for other operational, legal, or regulatory reasons. We will notify you of any significant changes by updating the date at the bottom of this policy.</p>

    <h2 class="mt-4">8. Contact Us</h2>
    <p>If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy, please contact us:</p>
    <p><strong>Email:</strong> <a href="mailto:support@yourwebsite.com">support@yourwebsite.com</a></p>

    <footer class="mt-5">
        <p class="text-muted">This Privacy Policy was last updated on <strong>October 4, 2024</strong>.</p>
    </footer>
</div>
